data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-22_">Here at ZUMI we're <span style="color: rgb(150, 155, 26); font-weight: bold;">happier on a healthy planet</span> which is why we have made it our personal responsibility to make all of our products and shipments <span style="text-decoration-line: underline;">carbon neutral.</span>&nbsp;It's undeniable that this planet is going to change. It has to. We don't get a choice. So it will either change by design or by disaster. That's the only choice we get in the matter... <span style="text-decoration-line: underline;">HOW</span> we will meet that change. <br><br><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(89, 97, 29);">And we choose by design.</span></span></p><div class="sc-iwajpm kydRHc pf-23_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-oeezt OJJCp pf-24_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-gXfVKN hOTIIO pf-25_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-27_">What does carbon neutral mean?</span></h2><p class="sc-TtZnY fPBQTR pf-28_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-30_">This means that we will eliminated, capture, or otherwise mitigate all of the carbon emissions created from both the production of our products to shipping them to your door.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iwajpm kydRHc pf-31_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-oeezt OJJCp pf-32_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-gXfVKN hOTIIO pf-33_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-35_">what is a carbon offset?</span></h2><p class="sc-TtZnY fPBQTR pf-36_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-38_">Carbon offsets are a practical and effective way to reduce the effects of climate change by funding, wind, solar and other renewable energy projects.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iwajpm kydRHc pf-39_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-oeezt OJJCp pf-40_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-gXfVKN hOTIIO pf-41_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-43_">how do i know where the money is going?</span></h2><p class="sc-TtZnY fPBQTR pf-44_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-46_">We have partnered with Cloverly for their informative and detailed work to offset carbon emissions. With them, we have access to projects that are permanent and without unintended consequences (i.e., creating more carbon elsewhere while in their efforts). All of the projects are independently certified to internationally recognized standards. These projects also include an element of social good, such as protecting endangered animals, or creating local jobs.<br><br>Every project is triple-verified, which means:<br><br>1. The project's financials, management team, project site, and carbon reduction method are carefully vetted.<br>2. At least one of the world's major carbon standards reviews the project.<br>3. Global Offset Research verifies the project against a second list of international standards.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iwajpm kydRHc pf-47_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-oeezt OJJCp pf-48_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-gXfVKN hOTIIO pf-49_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-51_">how do i know which project my order funded?</span></h2><p class="sc-TtZnY fPBQTR pf-52_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-54_">Once your items have been placed in your cart, you'll find a message above the checkout button that reads "Your delivery is carbon neutral with Cloverly!"<br><br>This message contains a link which will take you to the project page associated with your order. Here you can find out the what, where, how's and why's of the project that your order will fund.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iwajpm kydRHc pf-55_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-oeezt OJJCp pf-56_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-gXfVKN hOTIIO pf-57_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-59_">How does a carbon offset project work?</span></h2><p class="sc-TtZnY fPBQTR pf-60_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-62_">Every donation funds a project that reduces greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions by  supporting renewable energy, forestry or clean water initiatives.&nbsp;<br><br>Cloverly offers us access to a diverse portfolio of projects that is constantly evolving to meet customer and market demand.</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iwajpm kydRHc pf-63_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-oeezt OJJCp pf-64_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-gXfVKN hOTIIO pf-65_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-67_">how do you find the emissions of each order?</span></h2><p class="sc-TtZnY fPBQTR pf-68_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eGJWMs gQYBcx pf-70_">With the help of Cloverly's real-time algorithm, we're able to calculate the carbon emissions from both manufacturing and shipping each unique order by looking at variables such as product type, general materials of the product, product weight, shipping distance and more.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-iwajpm kydRHc pf-71_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="s